Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.75,0:00:04.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天要招待各位贵宾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.68,0:00:06.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有好吃的料理 饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.18,0:00:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有表演
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.19,0:00:08.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表演？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.49,0:00:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唱歌 跳舞和变魔术
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.36,0:00:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害 灯里你会这么多东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.82,0:00:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我不会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.79,0:00:16.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我以为蓝华你会的说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.73,0:00:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.93,0:00:18.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危机了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.42,0:00:45.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱 在AQUA的日历上 今天开始就是秋天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.12,0:00:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们领航员也换上了冬装制服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.93,0:00:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 亚利亚社长…你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.17,0:01:00.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从早到晚都非常舒适宜人的这几个月
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.91,0:01:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被称为秋天的观光季节
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:07.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再加上那个节日的到来 城中的人会开始变多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.65,0:01:11.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凤尾舟要通过啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.29,0:01:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那边如何了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.09,0:03:05.10,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(320,270)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那个 邂逅的结晶…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:09.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.67,0:03:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.74,0:03:14.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.34,0:03:17.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了啊 比平时更呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 前辈今天好像没什么精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.28,0:03:28.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实…小爱一直都没回我电邮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.09,0:03:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 她好像跟你说她奶奶身体不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.29,0:03:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.26,0:03:39.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.10,0:03:43.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她不是说要来参加Redentore的庆典吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.10,0:03:43.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs23}Redentore：每年7月的第三个星期六举行的庆典 Redentore\N意为「救世主耶稣基督」 庆典当日会从Zattere筑起船桥通往\NGiudecca的Redentore教会供人们前往参拜 晚上则举行烟花大会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.90,0:03:47.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 说是想看我的新凤尾舟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.18,0:03:52.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是她学业太忙碌了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天大概就会回我电邮了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.91,0:03:55.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.18,0:03:59.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一周就到Redentore了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.45,0:04:01.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:05.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈们今年打算怎么过Redentore呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.36,0:04:09.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姬屋每年都会开公司派对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:11.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我可能会跟晃前辈在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:13.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里前辈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.30,0:04:19.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去年接到艾莉西亚前辈的熟客的邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.17,0:04:24.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年小爱要是能来的话 我打算跟她一起过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:28.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 话说小后辈去年是怎么过的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:30.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡过的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.98,0:04:32.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.12,0:04:33.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡过的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.39,0:04:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明过节的说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.49,0:04:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为Redentore不是彻夜狂欢的节日嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.13,0:04:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第二天还要去上学的说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.13,0:04:45.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那倒是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.66,0:04:46.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太遗憾了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:51.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 今年的话第二天是休息日 所以没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.51,0:05:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.22,0:05:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晃前辈跟雅典娜前辈也在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.59,0:05:12.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有种不好的预感…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.53,0:05:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…三大精灵为何会聚在一起呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.07,0:05:24.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说 又是特训吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.70,0:05:26.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.07,0:05:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特训吗 嗯 也可以这么说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:39.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 灯里 我要提问了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.42,0:05:40.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.69,0:05:41.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Redentore是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.05,0:05:44.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…Redentore就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:48.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球的威尼斯城的贵族之间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.26,0:05:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,率先展开的夏日庆典…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.99,0:05:55.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家坐在各种各样的船上 一起玩乐到天亮…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:06:00.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后慢慢地演变成了新威尼斯初秋的风景诗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.94,0:06:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有点结巴 不过勉强算合格了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.64,0:06:06.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.75,0:06:13.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…莫非今年是我们六个人一起过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.15,0:06:14.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噗噗！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.29,0:06:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里你们三个负责招待客人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.66,0:06:22.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,负责招待客人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了准备饭菜和饮料之外
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:28.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要负责内部装饰和活动的时间表
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.60,0:06:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很值得一试呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:33.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一次能招待很多客人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.91,0:06:35.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是大显身手的好机会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.74,0:06:40.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传统料理的调味 还有配合饭菜口味的饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.98,0:06:42.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会很烦恼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.68,0:06:43.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.58,0:06:44.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:45.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.65,0:06:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实啊 我们特别为你们三个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.15,0:06:51.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好了Redentore专用的大船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.69,0:06:54.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是修行啊 修行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.16,0:06:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.03,0:06:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.63,0:06:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:05.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 真是伤脑筋…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.24,0:07:08.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办啊 蓝华
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.17,0:07:13.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠我们三个人真的能安排好一艘大船吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不安啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.98,0:07:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能做好吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.52,0:07:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:22.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天好早啊 小后辈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.69,0:07:24.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放学后直接过来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.99,0:07:27.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 因为想尽快给两位前辈看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.66,0:07:31.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天午休的时候我试着做了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.36,0:07:35.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我们大船的邀请函？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.47,0:07:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.84,0:07:41.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好厉害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.04,0:07:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 爱丽丝 这个很可爱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.91,0:07:45.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.64,0:07:51.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非你其实很期待Redentore的修行吗 爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.68,0:07:53.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.09,0:07:58.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 既然如此 就要好好地干
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:08:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会加油的 爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:02.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会超级加油的说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.93,0:08:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会输的～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.16,0:08:05.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.83,0:08:10.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先把饭菜和饮料放到最后去想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.40,0:08:13.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先决定要邀请谁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:18.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大船的搭载人数 加上我们一共能乘12人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.98,0:08:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:21.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还能请9个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:26.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈 晃前辈和雅典娜前辈不能漏掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:30.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邮递员大叔 晓先生和伍迪先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.79,0:08:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 灯里 你要好好想想哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.96,0:08:37.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你好像很多朋友的说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:40.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那蓝华想请谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.13,0:08:42.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿鲁之类的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.57,0:08:47.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.71,0:08:49.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.94,0:08:52.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.71,0:08:53.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祖母
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.78,0:08:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们明天就把邀请函发出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.45,0:09:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还能再请一个 找谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.35,0:09:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…我想请小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超级赞成的说 但是来得及吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.33,0:09:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 离Redentore只有一周了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.13,0:09:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 她说绝对要来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:19.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想等她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:23.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.24,0:09:28.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 那我再给她发一个邀请函的电邮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到Redentore的话 就是鸭肉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.82,0:09:36.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题在于怎么腌制啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:41.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 太硬的话老年人会咬不动的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.26,0:09:48.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用鱼和蔬菜来平衡一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:49.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.81,0:09:55.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:58.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祖母喜不喜欢蘑菇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.31,0:10:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之我们都试着做做看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.08,0:10:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.25,0:10:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.05,0:10:09.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在试做料理期间 虽然充满了不安和失败
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.29,0:10:10.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 灯里！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:13.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们所做的一切 都是前所未有地新奇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.89,0:10:15.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让时间飞快地溜走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:41.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了让我们邀请的客人 能够享受那欢乐的一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:44.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们心怀这样的愿景 积极地做着准备
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.02,0:10:50.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的日子非常充实而有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:10:59.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在非常期待节日的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.94,0:11:09.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 Redentore的日子到来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.72,0:11:14.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们兴奋期待的真正登场
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.73,0:11:32.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是…谁都不来的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:36.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱到最后都没跟我联系呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.51,0:11:39.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.14,0:11:42.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 邮递员大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.25,0:11:46.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以上船了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.45,0:11:47.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:48.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎您
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.49,0:11:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 我第一名吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.86,0:11:54.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是这次邀请的回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:56.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.36,0:11:57.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.06,0:12:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬓子 我们来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:04.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:06.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎二位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.84,0:12:12.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀 晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:14.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.41,0:12:17.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内部装饰还算过关吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.72,0:12:18.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:21.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请吧请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 大家这边请
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:27.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.96,0:12:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那个超级像雅典娜的风格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.03,0:12:30.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.80,0:12:35.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.53,0:12:36.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 阿鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.07,0:12:38.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 你来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.87,0:12:40.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢招待
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.97,0:12:42.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这么晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.67,0:12:43.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 上衣给我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.88,0:12:46.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 工作迟迟完成不了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.78,0:12:49.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就应该先跟我说一声啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:53.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁啊 在那边玩新婚夫妇对话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.79,0:12:55.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了 马尾男
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.32,0:12:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祖母
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.52,0:13:00.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.99,0:13:04.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 呀 真热闹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.10,0:13:06.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您这边请
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.90,0:13:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了呢 爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.24,0:13:13.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我家种的麝香葡萄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.24,0:13:15.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:17.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.34,0:13:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.14,0:13:21.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都这么精神实在太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:27.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱还没来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.99,0:13:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 差不多该把船划出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.90,0:13:40.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.24,0:14:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.98,0:14:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.05,0:14:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:35.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.09,0:14:44.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱 我还以为你不会来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.20,0:14:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你奶奶的身体怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.97,0:14:50.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 已经好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.80,0:14:53.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想给你惊喜 所以没跟你联系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:54.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我出差顺便把她带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:15:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但比预定的时间稍晚了一点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.81,0:15:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 您是小爱的姐姐的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.18,0:15:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是她姐姐的丈夫 敦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次真是谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.12,0:15:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.92,0:15:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉 我现在马上要去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.79,0:15:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能否请你们帮忙照顾爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.23,0:15:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 当然欢迎之至
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.26,0:15:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就拜托几位了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.80,0:15:23.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.98,0:15:41.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.05,0:15:43.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.79,0:15:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.62,0:15:48.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好像很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.06,0:15:50.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想快点开饭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.06,0:15:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子开始饿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.03,0:15:55.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀 摆得好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.70,0:15:57.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外表很是不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.30,0:16:04.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 各位客人 今天欢迎来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:07.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…虽然仅仅是一点心意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.45,0:16:10.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望大家能够共同度过这初秋之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们无比地荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.35,0:16:18.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 为这美好的Redentore
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.32,0:16:20.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干杯～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.86,0:16:22.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.04,0:16:35.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 这是什么菜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.21,0:16:38.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是烤鸭和煮得软软的荷兰豆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.44,0:16:43.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个泡菜放了好多蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.65,0:16:45.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,味道非常奢华呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.38,0:16:48.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 谢谢您的夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.45,0:16:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烤饭团…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.89,0:16:53.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请您尝尝看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.33,0:16:58.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢挑战我的得意料理 胆子不小嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.30,0:17:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在里面夹了烧肉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.21,0:17:08.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合格
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.11,0:17:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.18,0:17:18.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱肚子饿了吧 要多吃点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.98,0:17:20.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.12,0:17:25.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个烧鸭可能不错的说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.12,0:17:31.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs24}注：日文鸭子（かも）和可能（かも）同音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.92,0:17:27.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是很不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:31.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 刚才那是用鸭子和可能来玩文字游戏…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.70,0:17:33.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 老头子的冷笑话禁止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.46,0:17:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.97,0:17:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一二 一二 一二
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.01,0:17:42.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛 余兴节目吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.97,0:17:46.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 接下来由我和亚利亚社长一起跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.69,0:18:01.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 我也要来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.60,0:18:12.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太完美了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.20,0:18:14.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鼓掌～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.83,0:18:45.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内部装饰很温馨 让大家都放松下来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.24,0:18:49.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 你们三人都很努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:18:58.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在一起待很长时间的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.72,0:19:01.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时大家的对话会暂时中断
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是非常自然而来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.29,0:19:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美好的静寂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.76,0:19:11.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常非常喜欢这样的气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:19.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里前辈 差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.84,0:19:20.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.74,0:19:22.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:23.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.98,0:19:28.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.51,0:19:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停电了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.58,0:20:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来已经12点了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.85,0:20:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把时间遗忘了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.95,0:20:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.49,0:20:11.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真难忘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.82,0:20:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不经意地关掉照明灯 很狡猾嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.10,0:20:22.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快 你们也都过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.77,0:20:24.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:27.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是祖母的邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.74,0:20:31.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:41.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都这么高兴 真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:42.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.97,0:21:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天能够得到邀请 真是谢谢你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.91,0:21:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托你们三人的福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们度过了一个非常开心的Redentore
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.25,0:21:12.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这些人 如果没有了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.42,0:21:14.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定就不会相识
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.65,0:21:16.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是美好邂逅的结晶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.66,0:21:22.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美好邂逅的…结晶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.09,0:21:25.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了给我们制造了这美丽一瞬的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.76,0:21:29.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,领航员的种子们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.53,0:21:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.18,0:21:47.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AQUA的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.19,0:21:50.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大海的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.99,0:21:52.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.59,0:21:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浪花和风的声音 我们终于相见了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.10,0:22:06.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.77,0:22:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能遇到灯里姐姐 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.58,0:22:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天我们一起去寻找AQUA的美好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.42,0:22:22.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？太好了～
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.19,0:22:25.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去「希望之丘」看看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.42,0:22:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还想坐坐水上电梯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.16,0:22:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,600)}还有啊 还有啊…我想去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.43,0:22:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被浪花送来的温馨一刻所包围
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.70,0:22:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这颗星球 或许会永远地守护着各种各样的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.02,0:24:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 雪白的温馨城市…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【OPJP】
